20left%20lakhs%20in%20crisis.%20Your%20donation%20will%20directly%20fund%20rescue%20boats%2C%20groceries%2C%20hygiene%20kits%2C%20and%20shelter%2C%20bringing%20hope%20to%20families%20who%20have%20lost%20almost%20everything.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496899%2Fhelp-punjab-floods-relief-and-rescue-operations-donatekart-the-better-india-campaign%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2230%20Years%2C%20101%20Elephant%20Corridors%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20Blueprint%20for%20Elephant%20Protection%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeatured%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepatriot.in%2Freports%2Fwhat-our-giant-nomads-need-16992%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Patriot%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20August%202024.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20decades%20ago%2C%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%2C%20a%20youth%20could%20be%20seen%20hiding%20high%20up%20in%20one%20of%20the%20watch%20towers.%20Anyone%20passing%20by%20would%20wonder%20about%20the%20unusual%20spot%20he%20had%20picked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496783%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20answer%20lay%20in%20an%20amusing%20scene%3B%20every%20time%20the%20young%20boy%20attempted%20to%20make%20his%20way%20out%20of%20the%20tower%2C%20an%20elephant%20(camouflaged%20by%20the%20thicket%20of%20bushes)%20would%20appear%20and%20charge%20at%20him.%20And%20once%20again%2C%20the%20boy%20would%20ascend%20the%20watch%20tower%20and%20wait.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20all%20of%20four%20hours%20before%20the%20elephant%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20move%2C%20and%20the%20youth%20finally%20descended%20the%20watch%20tower%2C%20relief%20colouring%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20in%20this%20story%20was%20a%20young%20Vivek%20Menon%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20dedicated%20to%20the%20preservation%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F236243%2Fganesh-chaturthi-wild-elephant-protection-love-heroes-conservation-protection-mahout-assam-tamil-nadu-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotection%20of%20wild%20habitats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20tryst%20with%20the%20elephant%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20made%20me%20understand%20the%20animal%E2%80%99s%20strength%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles%2C%20quick%20to%20add%2C%20however%2C%20that%20his%20love%20for%20the%20wild%20and%20nature%20predates%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20singular%20story%20that%20served%20as%20inspiration%20to%20become%20a%20conservationist%2C%20Menon%20insists.%20But%20coax%20him%20a%20little%2C%20and%20he%20says%20genetics%20did%20play%20its%20role%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20from%20Kerala%2C%20the%20land%20of%20elephants%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20as%20did%20childhood%20treks.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20were%20treks%20to%20the%20Himalayas%20during%20my%20school%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Menon%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20right%20to%20say%20that%20I%20took%20to%20animals%20and%20birds%20the%20moment%20I%20was%20exposed%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20room%20resembled%20an%20animal%20shelter.%20Birds%20and%20small%20animals%20rescued%20from%20the%20wild%20and%20predatory%20hands%20found%20a%20safe%20space.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20I%20was%20doing%20them%20%5Bthe%20animals%5D%20good%20by%20bringing%20them%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20justifies.%20Today%2C%20at%2056%2C%20the%20conservationist%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20that%20same%20goodwill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHow%20many%20hours%20I%20have%20spent%20watching%20young%20bulls%20playfully%20test%20their%20strength%2C%20their%20nascent%20ivories%20never%20inflicting%20harm%2C%20their%20trunks%20loosely%20entwined%20%26amp%3B%20ears%20aflap%20while%20muscle%20and%20sinew%20grind%20against%20the%20other.%20These%20young%20mock-battles%20train%20them%20for%20later%20adult%20life!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEm9soIlOnY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FEm9soIlOnY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Vivek%20Menon%20(%40vivek4wild)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvivek4wild%2Fstatus%2F1802908763894186253%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F171244%2Fkarnataka-farmer-forest-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20for%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20when%20he%20digressed%20from%20the%20career%20plans%20his%20father%20had%20for%20him%20%E2%80%94%20a%20career%20in%20automobile%20engineering%20%E2%80%94%20and%20followed%20his%20heart%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20zoology%20laboratory%2C%20no%20one%20was%20shocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20concerning%20animals%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestion%3A%20Is%20there%20a%20better%20way%20to%20interview%20a%20conservationist%20than%20reaching%20him%20through%20a%20Zoom%20call%20while%20he%20is%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20South%20African%20jungle%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbsolutely%20not%3B%20just%20what%20is%20needed%20to%20add%20essence%20to%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMenon%E2%80%99s%20excitement%20was%20palpable.%20As%20senior%20advisor%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98International%20Fund%20for%20Animal%20Welfare%E2%80%99%20for%20years%20now%2C%20he%20was%20in%20the%20Southern%20African%20country%20assisting%20in%20an%20operation%20that%20involved%20radio%20collaring%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F260553%2Fwildlife-conservation-elephants-save-school-teacher-hero-west-bengal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelephants%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20process%20in%20which%20a%20collar%20with%20an%20attached%20radio%20transmitter%20is%20put%20on%20an%20animal%20so%20that%20its%20movements%20in%20its%20natural%20habitat%20can%20be%20remotely%20monitored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20he%20jokingly%20adds%2C%20my%20interview%20call%20is%20interrupting%20something%20very%20important%20that%20he%E2%80%99d%20otherwise%20be%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20watching%20150%20elephants%20against%20the%20setting%20sun%20in%20Zimbabwe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%20has%20watched%20Menon%20around%20elephants%20would%20testify%20that%20the%20two%20share%20a%20bond.%20He%20understands%20them.%20And%20the%20relationship%20is%20reciprocal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubstantial%20proof%20of%20his%20love%20for%20the%20wild%20lies%20in%20the%20five%20organisations%20that%20he%20has%20created%20%E2%80%94%20TRAFFIC%20India%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wildlife%20trade%20monitoring%20network%3B%20NGO%20Srishti%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20founded%20to%20protect%20the%20environment%20in%20Delhi%3B%20Delhi%20Bird%20Club%3B%20Venu%20Menon%20Animal%20Allies%20Foundation%3B%20and%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20(WTI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wild%20elephant%20herd%20in%20Keonjhar%2C%20Odisha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360931%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20wild%20elephant%20herd%20in%20Keonjhar%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPicture%20a%20world%20where%20trade%20in%20wild%20plants%20and%20animals%20is%20managed%20at%20sustainable%20levels%20without%20damaging%20the%20integrity%20of%20ecological%20systems.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20TRAFFIC%20India%20has%20attempted%20to%20do%20since%20the%20outset.%20Menon%20who%20co-founded%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F48373%2Fwildlife-trade-trafficking-india-humane-society%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20trade%20monitoring%20%3C%2Fa%3Enetwork%20with%20his%20colleague%20and%20legendary%20conservationist%20Ashok%20Kumar%2C%20emphasises%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20resolve%20to%20bust%20poaching%20amid%20other%20illegal%20activities.%20The%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20work%20also%20extends%20to%20the%20fight%20against%20illegal%20international%20ivory%20trade.%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20work%20earned%20him%20the%20RG%20Samsara%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20activism%20is%20important%2C%20this%20biologist%20believes%20in%20shedding%20an%20equal%20spotlight%20on%20creating%20impact%20through%20policy%20frameworks.%20As%20Chair%20of%20the%20Asian%20Elephant%20Specialist%20Group%20for%20the%20IUCN%20(International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature)%20for%20the%20past%2012%20years%2C%20Menon%20elaborates%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20work%20in%20advising%20various%20governments%20on%20%E2%80%9Cdoing%20things%20right%20for%20elephants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20includes%20bringing%20out%20scientific%20work%2C%20guidelines%2C%20and%20manuals.%20It%20also%20includes%20planning%20linear%20infrastructure%3B%20highways%2C%20railways%2C%20road%20passes%2C%20and%20power%20lines%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20the%20elephants%20are%20allowed%20to%20pass%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20segues%20into%20the%20topic%20of%20identifying%20and%20protecting%20elephant%20corridors%2C%20a%20brainchild%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20overarching%20goal%20being%20to%20secure%20a%20%E2%80%98rite%20of%20passage%E2%80%99%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F188598%2Felephant-doctor-assam-treats-hundreds-wildlife-hero-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig%20mammals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20WTI%20along%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20top%20scientists%20have%20identified%20and%20surveyed%20101%20such%20functional%20corridors%20across%2011%20states%20for%20the%2029%2C000%20odd%20Asian%20Elephants%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20a%20spare%20bedroom%20project%20to%20a%20phenomenal%20trust%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202023%20study%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20Wildlife%20and%20Biodiversity%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20corridors%20are%20short%20strips%20of%20forests%20that%20link%20two%20larger%20parts%20of%20the%20forest%3B%20like%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccontinuous%20two-dimensional%20landscape%20structure%20that%20interconnects%20two%20or%20more%20previously%20linked%20areas%20of%20animal%20habitats%E2%80%9D.%20These%20enable%20the%20animals%20to%20disperse%2C%20reduce%20their%20risk%20of%20separation%20and%20make%20habitat%20rehabilitation%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20explored%20how%20anthropogenic%20stress%2C%20the%20development%20of%20roads%20and%20railways%2C%20and%20hydroelectric%20projects%20are%20hampering%20these%20corridors.%20The%20problem%20is%20compounded%20by%20multiple%20forests%20being%20turned%20into%20croplands%20by%20the%20farming%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-500x417.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20walking%20bear%20cubs%20to%20reintroducing%20orphaned%20elephant%20calves%20back%20into%20the%20wild%2C%20Vivek%20Menon%20is%20championing%20wildlife%20conservation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-